{"word":"G4121 - πλεονάζω - pleonázō - pleh-on-ad'-zo - Abound","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πλεονάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pleonázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pleh-on-ad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Abound</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பெருகு"},{"paragraph":"1. to superabound (to have over)"},{"paragraph":"2. to make to increase"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4119 - πλείων - pleíōn - pli-own/4119\">G4119</a>; to <i>do</i>, <i>make</i> or <i>be more</i>, that is, <i>increase</i> (transitively or intransitively); by extension to <i>superabound:</i> - abound, abundant, make to increase, have over.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4121/4121\">G4121</a>, <a href=\"#/G4122/4122\">G4122</a>, <a href=\"#/G4123/4123\">G4123</a>, <a href=\"#/G5250/5250\">G5250</a>"}]}